name: Gardeners London
overview: Gardeners London is a top company in providing gardening services. Do you need professional lawn mowing? Or may be hedge trimming is what you need? It is never mind for us because we can fulfill all the possible tasks related to gardening. Our gardeners are only professionals with the needed qualification and experience. What is more beautiful than a well cleaned house with well maintained garden? Make your garden looks better and improve the appearance of your property. And all this on the most attractive prices in London with the possibility to tailor our services and be sure that you pay only for what you receive. Call us or send us an e-mail for an absolutely free quote!We service the areas of Marylebone, Paddington, Bayswater, Acton, Chiswick, Ealing, Hammersmith, Hanwell, Kensington, Maida Hill, Notting Hill, Brixton, Chelsea, Clapham, Stockwell, Fulham, Battersea, Balham, Barnes, Mortlake, Putney, Streatham, Tooting, Earlsfield, Southfields, Wimbledon.
